Wikinegata [arnaout2021wikinegata,arnaout2021negative] is a tool for browsing more than 600m negations about 0.5m Wikidata entities. It gives insights into the peer-based method [arnaout020enriching] where users can inspect different peers used to infer certain negations (see Figure (ref)). In commonsense KBs, the Uncommonsense system [arnaoutcikm2022] provide a similar experience about everyday concepts.